name.@value: University Of Melbourne, Louise Hanson-Dyer Music Library: Rare Collections

openingHours.@value: Twenty-four hours notice must be given prior to viewing by either visiting, phoning (03) 8344 4219 or sending an email to the Louise Hanson-Dyer Music Library. Items are viewed in the Cultural Collections Reading Room located on the third floor of the Baillieu Library.
